Per-offline discussion with [~jingzhao], we should keep the {{validate()}} method signature as it-was. The reason was that it's a public API and downstream applications may call it directly before calling setters. The v1 patch is to make the code similar to pre- [HDFS-10397]. The changes are:
# Ignore the {{delete}} option if {{useDiff}} is set. This is processed in both {{setDeleteMissing()}} and {{setUseDiff()}}
